# (D) Agent OS-direct shims — keychain, systray, browser launcher.
*/packages/agent/internal/identity/keystore
*/packages/agent/internal/host/trayipc
*/packages/agent/internal/host/openbrowser

# (D) agent/cmd/agent/platformshim — re-categorized 2026-05-21 from (A)
# to (D) (E85 D-4). 16 files split across //go:build darwin / linux /
# windows / !X. Functions invoke:
#   - macOS `security add-trusted-cert` (System Keychain) via catrust
#   - Linux `update-ca-certificates` (root + system trust store)
#   - Windows SCM `mgr.OpenService` + `MessageBoxW` UI prompts
#   - SystemExtensions bundle inventory (/Library/SystemExtensions/<UUID>)
#   - NE bridge XPC over Darwin-only socket
# None testable in unit scope; covered by /build-agent + per-platform
# install/uninstall smoke + the integration suite.
*/packages/agent/cmd/agent/platformshim

# (D) agent/ui — Wails desktop app entry. `//go:embed all:frontend/dist`
# requires `npm run build` on the Wails frontend before `go test` can
# even compile the main package. Build chain belongs to the Agent release
# pipeline (`Skill('build-agent')`), not the unit-test runner.
*/packages/agent/ui

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# (E) Network-infra-bound — real S3, NATS, Valkey Sentinel, live TLS.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# (E) Real S3 client; tested via /smoke-gateway with spillstore enabled.
*/packages/shared/storage/spillstore/s3

# (E) Real NATS JetStream client; tested via /test-all (which spins
# JetStream in docker-compose).
*/packages/shared/transport/mq

# (E) Live TLS handshake required (bumping leaf certs through the
# compliance-proxy CA); tested via /test-compliance-proxy.
*/packages/shared/transport/tlsbump

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# (F) Integration-only — existing *_integration_test.go behind build tag.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# (F) agent/internal/platform — integration tests behind a build tag;
# concrete impls live in `darwin/`, `linux/`, `windows/` sub-pkgs and
# require OS-level packet-capture / NE bridge / WinDivert. Sub-pkg
# tests cover the actual logic; the root pkg only re-exports.
*/packages/agent/internal/platform

# ai-gateway/internal/ingress/proxy: removed 2026-05-21 — now 95.1%
# (E85 D-5 closure). 7 fakeexec-driven tests in proxy_fakeexec_test.go +
# proxy_residuals_test.go covered the last non-cache-HIT branches:
# DryRun rate-limited 429 / Coerced header stamp / E57 reverse-decode
# success / CacheReadTokens=0→ProviderCacheMiss / CacheCreationTokens
# audit stamp / Embeddings dimension metadata / nil-Usage guard in
# provcoreUsageToMap. L2 semantic-cache HIT path is still unit-untested
# but the package now crosses 95% without needing the exemption;
# /smoke-gateway --all-ingress covers the cache-HIT integration.

